text:
Hidden in an industry area @ kim san leng kopitiam. Come here to try the jb tai pai tong. Ordered
san lou meehoon 三楼米粉，
Stir-fry Chives 青龙菜 and
kam heong lala 甘香啦啦。

Very authentic and the portion is quite big, price is affordable also

Parking was accessible and easy to identify the location. Food selection wise was good. As the location is near factories and industrial, the air
Quality is not that tip top. If its just for a meal, Overall is acceptable.
All are good and fair price
Newly open Lai kee… must try it
